                            <div class="clr"></div>
                            <div class="testi">
                                <p>
                                    <span class="q"><img src="~/Images/qoute_1.gif" width="20" height="15" alt="" /></span>
                                    We can let circumstances rule us, or we can take charge and rule our lives from within.
